KitKat3::
She smiled. "I'm sorry. It's just that, well, I miss all that I used 
to do.  I mean, I miss the feeling of the pack. Everything is so 
different. I'm sorry. I didn't mean to get you down." She kisses his 
hand and closed her eyes.  She missed that wonderful feeling of being 
in love as well.  She did still love him, but, her programming was 
different now.  Now she had the urge to kill the maximals more than 
to be in love with Drillbit.  Little did she know that the prgram was 
Squizzy's idea. 



Feline::
"OK, pick a place and we'll meet."  She looked down, she still had 
the wings he had given her.  She smiled at it. "Yeah, when can we 
meet and where?"
